    {
      "Text": "Security update for python-python-engineio",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for python-python-engineio fixes the following issues:\n\nChanges in python-python-engineio:\n\n- CVE-2026-48802: remote user can cause the creation of unnecessary\n  background threads in the server through the heartbeat mechanism\n  and cause a DoS (bsc#1269544)\n- CVE-2026-48809: size of incoming messages is not checked before\n  they are loaded into memory and allows remote users to cause a DoS\n  via excessive memory allocation (bsc#1269545)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
